description:
A man who must atone for a tragic mistake by saving a little girl from a ruthless, undead preacher.

A man's life is thrown into disarray after the death of his daughter. His emotional scars begin to heal when he meets a young woman but when she is kidnapped he must face the dilemma of sinking further into alcoholism or getting it together to save the girl and his newfound reason to live...
